# Canonical URLs: no trailing slash (except /)
#
# This site uses Astro `build.format: "file"` so each route is emitted as
# `*.html` (e.g. `/terms.html`). Cloudflare Pages will serve extensionless URLs
# from matching HTML files and redirect `/terms.html -> /terms` by default, so
# we only need to canonicalize trailing-slash variants back to the clean URL.

/terms/ /terms 301
/privacy/ /privacy 301
/cookies/ /cookies 301
/disclaimer/ /disclaimer 301

/blog/ /blog 301
/blog/*/ /blog/:splat 301
